{"tid":2339613,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕鉅作：《如果我是莫湛深》","createTime":"2020-12-24T18:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T01:10:57.000Z","uid":199081,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4298431e731dbd1720ed79f063ea2e9be3cef821","tid":2339613,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T18:53:28.000Z","msg":"《如果我是莫湛深》<br />\n<br />\n九巴飛站車長廢人　逼使N賓報復放針<br />\n滑牛兩打淋贈送眾神　為侮辱反轉清真<br />\n<br />\n過百分身帳當複製人　有幕後指示遊走兩登<br />\n熱血公民黃洋達似偉文　再永續吹奏云根<br />\n<br />\n如果我是莫湛深　這句話太吸引<br />\n犯罪在鎂光下能扮冇心<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=48925fe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n是打手亦是政棍一個　日能日喺呢度吹捧大亨<br />\n<br />\n下期預告：<br />\n《香港針晨》<br />\n莫湛深 係N賓 九巴去 又放針..."},{"pid":"e9b539db16cc025cb897904517ca48dfef0f4515","tid":2339613,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T18:54:23.000Z","msg":"見到莫乜乜以為係木耳po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6967164cee932f1445c550e75d44e7af5a6cedab","tid":2339613,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803896312d607643d787e465ab9d2700326eb5c7","tid":2339613,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:44:01.000Z","msg":"咁夜冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467b17b04d42910b7f983f117e02aa7786925ed7","tid":2339613,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa82997660a8e5f955a3a94e3582c72766f2a64","tid":2339613,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"803896312d607643d787e465ab9d2700326eb5c7","tid":2339613